azureLogAnalytics.query:
customMetrics
| where name == "altinn_app_oed_send_correspondence_item" and customDimensions.itemType == "ProbateIssuedItem"
| summarize sum(value)

let banks = dynamic({"984851006":"DNB", "952706365":"SB1 Nord-Norge", "920058817":"Nordea", "920426530": "SB1 Østlandet", "937901003": "SB1 SMN", "937895321": "SB1 Sør-Norge"});
customMetrics 
| where cloud_RoleName == "oed" and name == "altinn_app_oed_dan_request" and value > 0
| summarize lastrequest=arg_max(timestamp, customDimensions) by dataset=tostring(customDimensions.dataSetName), orgNr=tostring(customDimensions.orgNr)    // Siste request utført pr dataset
| join kind=fullouter ( 
  customMetrics 
  | where cloud_RoleName == "oed" and name == "altinn_app_oed_dan_error" and value > 0
  | summarize lasterror=arg_max(timestamp, customDimensions) by dataset=tostring(customDimensions.dataSetName), orgNr=tostring(customDimensions.orgNr)    // Siste error registrert pr dataset
  )
  on dataset
| project dataset, name=iff(isnull(banks[orgNr]), orgNr, banks[orgNr]), lastrequest, lasterror, isOk = isnull(lasterror) or lasterror < lastrequest

requests
| where cloud_RoleName == "oed" and url !contains "/health" and customDimensions contains "user.id"
| summarize value=count() by client_OS, client_Browser
| sort by value

requests
| where cloud_RoleName == "oed" and $__timeFilter(timestamp)
| project userPartyId=tostring(customDimensions.['user.party.id']), 
          instanceOwnerPartyId=tostring(customDimensions.['instance.owner.party.id'])
| where isnotempty(userPartyId) and isnotempty(instanceOwnerPartyId)
| summarize ['Unike brukere']=dcount(userPartyId), ['Unike dødsbo']=dcount(instanceOwnerPartyId)

customMetrics
| where name == "altinn_app_oed_send_correspondence_item"
| project timestamp, value, customDimensions.itemType
| summarize sum(value) by bin(timestamp, 1m), tostring(customDimensions_itemType)
| project timestamp, sum_value, customDimensions_itemType
| project-rename sum=sum_value
| order by timestamp asc

customMetrics
| where name == "altinn_app_oed_handle_event"
| project timestamp, value, customDimensions.eventType
| summarize sum(value) by bin(timestamp, 1m), tostring(customDimensions_eventType)
| project timestamp, sum_value, customDimensions_eventType
| project-rename _=sum_value
| order by timestamp asc

customMetrics
| where name == "altinn_app_oed_post_event"
| project timestamp, value, customDimensions.eventType
| summarize sum(value) by bin(timestamp, 1m), tostring(customDimensions_eventType)
| project timestamp, sum_value, customDimensions_eventType
| project-rename _=sum_value
| order by timestamp asc

customMetrics
| where name startswith "altinn_app_oed_dan_request"
| project timestamp, value, customDimensions.dataSetName
| summarize sum(value) by bin(timestamp, 1m), tostring(customDimensions_dataSetName)
//| project timestamp, sum_value, customDimensions_dataSetName
| project-rename _=sum_value
| order by timestamp asc

customMetrics
| where name startswith "altinn_app_oed_dan_error"
| project timestamp, value, customDimensions.dataSetName
| summarize sum(value) by bin(timestamp, 1m), tostring(customDimensions_dataSetName)
//| project timestamp, sum_value, customDimensions_dataSetName
| project-rename _=sum_value
| order by timestamp asc
